title: Funkey
description:
Inspired by a guy in the forum and the music is by him. Just start the Funkey.exe and every time someone presses down the <backspace>,<E>,or <A> it will play the tune funkey town. If you want to quit the program just press ctr-alt-del and go to processes and end the process funkey.exe.Source is included in download will only work on windows even if not using compiled program because of an os specific module.

GL
-EAnder
